  .section.banner
    .row
      .col-12.col-md-6.offset-md-3
        .text-center
          = image_tag 'alex_smith_pixelized.png', id: 'headshot', class: 'circle-image', onmouseover: "this.src='/images/alex_smith_wink_pixelized.png'", onmouseout: "this.src='/images/alex_smith_pixelized.png'"
    .row.mb-5
      .col-12.col-md-6.offset-md-3.text-center
        %h2#intro-text
          I've been called many things...
        %h1#type-text
        %h2#name-text
          But you can call me
        #name.hvr-float-shadow
          Alex
  #about.section.about-me-summary
    .row.mb-5
      .col-12.col-md-8.offset-md-2
        %h3
          TLDR
        %p
          A borderline cold brew coffee addict and a Florida native currently
          residing in Los Angeles, California, my name is Alexander Smith (Alex).
          If I had to describe a
          %em "personal mission statement"
          , I'd say that mine is to provide others with opportunities -
          especially if it helps them move up the so-called socio-economic
          ladder.
        %p
          While I call Tampa home, I was born in Baltimore, MD and I've
          been to Germany more times than my fingers permit me to count. I have a
          black belt in Taekwondo (it's been awhile though). I originally planned
          to join the military and was in ROTC in High School. My friends call me
          an adrenaline junkie because I love anything with an engine. I've had
          experience with 4-wheelers, go-karts, boats, jet skis, motorcycles,
          sports cars, and more. If it goes fast, I'm interested. Speaking of
          interested, want to learn more?  You can read more about...
        %p
          %a{ href: '#past' } How I went from flipping burgers at the neighborhood DQ to Wall Street.
        %p
          %a{ href: '#present' } How I retired from being a corporate mercenary and became a Full-Stack Developer at a startup.
        %p
          %a{ href: '#future' } What I'm working towards next.
        %p
          And while we're still talking about me, you can
          %a{ href: 'https://hirealexsmith.com' } hire me
          to help
          = succeed '!' do
            %span{ style: 'font-style: italic;' } you

    .row
      .col-12.col-md-8.offset-md-2
        %h3
          Quick timeline of professional experience
        %p
          Clicking on the company titles will take you to the section of my story
          describing the position. You can also check out my resume
          = succeed "." do
            %a{ href: '/alex_smith_resume.pdf', target: '_blank' } here
          = partial 'partials/experience_links'

