  .section
    .row
      .col-12.col-md-8.offset-md-2
        %h3
          Where I am
        %p.about-me-quote
          %i.fa.fa-quote-left.fa-3x.fa-pull-left
          Our DNA is 96% chimpanzee. Is that even worth arguing?! If I gave
          you a sandwich that was filled with 96% sh*t and 4% ham, would you
          be willing to consider that a ham sandwich? So If you ever start
          taking things too seriously, just remember that we are talking monkeys
          on an organic spaceship flying through the universe. - Joe Rogan
        %br
        %p.about-me-text
